{"tid":2372580,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果能夠讓你失去感受苦與樂情緒 你會唔會接受？","createTime":"2021-01-19T20:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:28:53.000Z","uid":4672,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f75b0bce47324ab61403bbcda994c344e0572efa","tid":2372580,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T20:08:09.000Z","msg":"唔會感受到痛苦 悲傷 苦悶 <br />\n唔會感受到快樂 幸福 成就感<br />\n<br />\n你大腦失去感性思考fonction<br />\n可以讓你不再有感受情緒 同反應情緒既能力<br />\n包括 唔會感受到自己同他人情緒波動<br />\n<br />\n從而徹底消滅痛苦 煩惱 苦悶 等一切負面情感<br />\n（當然亦同時消滅快樂 幸福等一切正面情感）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個純理性思考人類 無痛苦 無苦悶 <br />\n你會接受/不接受？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不接受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6c367fb248968aed4e07f30d35f5e130777487","tid":2372580,"uid":350157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"咁樣做人冇意思架啦 會咩都唔想追求.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28706e8a3d133e2a519e422f073e77df9ff65dd7","tid":2372580,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T20:53:43.000Z","msg":"印象中有人對老鼠做過類似實驗，損毀左老鼠個獎勵系統，冇幾耐就因為冇食野死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdd27f1746492ac32954b919037eeeca93608cd","tid":2372580,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6c367fb248968aed4e07f30d35f5e130777487","tid":2372580,"uid":350157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T20:10:49.000Z","msg":"咁樣做人冇意思架啦 會咩都唔想追求.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T21:52:58.000Z","msg":"但做人本來就沒咩意思  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生意義只係一場自我安慰既打稻草人遊戲"},{"pid":"a135c41f5fce7b7cfbba25c3956c59ea4ec9912f","tid":2372580,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike